{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_017HHys9mDmEXF26fRkgrXGt","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01UvHxAaYc1qJ25jsjgScwY5","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Rosemary Focaccia Bread.generated.22.txt","content":"ROSEMARY\nFOCACCIA\nBREAD\n\nMakes 2 loaves | Active time: 20 min | Passive time: 2-3 hours (includes proofing)\n\nDOUGH:\n500g strong bread flour\n350ml warm water\n7g instant yeast\n10g salt\n30ml olive oil\n\nTOPPING:\n6 tbsp olive oil\n3 tbsp coarse sea salt\n4 sprigs fresh rosemary\nCracked black pepper\n\nMETHOD - DOUGH:\n1. In large bowl, combine flour, yeast, and salt. Mix well.\n2. Add water and oil. Mix until shaggy dough forms.\n3. Knead by hand for 10 minutes or with stand mixer for 6 minutes until smooth and elastic.\n4. Place in oiled bowl, cover with damp cloth. Let rise at room temperature for 90 minutes until doubled.\n\nSHAPING:\n1. Turn dough onto lightly floured surface. Divide into two equal pieces.\n2. Shape each into a rough rectangle about 25cm x 20cm.\n3. Transfer to two oiled sheet pans or one large pan.\n4. Cover loosely and let rise for 60 minutes until puffy.\n\nTOPPING & BAKING:\n1. Preheat oven to 220°C. With oiled fingertips, dimple entire surface of dough, creating characteristic indentations.\n2. Drizzle generously with olive oil. Sprinkle sea salt over surface.\n3. Strip leaves from rosemary sprigs, scatter over dough. Add cracked pepper.\n4. Bake for 20-25 minutes until golden brown and crispy at edges.\n5. Cool slightly before serving warm.\n\nSTORAGE: Best eaten same day. Wrap tightly—keeps 2 days. Refreshes beautifully when wrapped in foil and warmed.\n\nTIPS: Do not skip the dimpling stage—it creates the signature focaccia texture. Water temperature should be around 37°C.\nFor herb variations, try thyme, oregano, or olives mixed into topping.\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":8,"cache_creation_input_tokens":891,"cache_read_input_tokens":108215,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":891},"output_tokens":7,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"10f3291a-c249-48df-81bc-02c14533ee15","uuid":"7ed6b883-8690-4da6-b5de-bdf68c69148d"}
